'''恆河'''（{{lang-sa|गङ्गा}}，{{lang-hi|गंगा}}，{{lang-ur|گنگا}}（Ganga）{{IPA-hns|ˈɡəŋɡaː|IPA|hi-Ganga.ogg}}；{{lang-ta|கங்கை}}，{{lang-bn|গঙ্গা}} Gônga，玄奘譯為'''殑伽河'''）是[[南亚|南亚]]的一条主要[[河流|河流]]，流經[[印度|印度]]北部及[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]。恒河源头[[帕吉勒提河|帕吉勒提河]]和[[阿勒格嫩达河|阿勒格嫩达河]]发源自印度[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]的[[根戈德里冰川|根戈德里]]等冰川，它横越北印度平原（即[[恒河平原|恒河平原]]），流经[[北方邦|北方邦]]，会合其最大支流[[亚穆纳河|亚穆纳河]]，再流经[[比哈尔邦|比哈尔邦]]、[[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]]，最后它分为多条分流注入[[孟加拉湾|孟加拉湾]]，其中一条是[[加尔各答|加尔各答]]附近的[[胡格利河|胡格利河]]，另外一条是进入[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]]的[[博多河|博多河]]，[[博多河|博多河]]进入孟加拉国后，会合[[布拉马普特拉河|布拉马普特拉河]]（中国境内为[[雅鲁藏布江|雅鲁藏布江]]）在孟加拉国境内的下游[[贾木纳河|贾木纳河]]，注入[[孟加拉湾|孟加拉湾]]，其入海河段称为[[梅格纳河|梅格纳河]]。支流布拉马普特拉河及其以上部分不算在内，恒河长为2,510公里，流域面积91万平方公里，达印度国土面积的三分之一，恆河也為世界河水流量前20大的河流之一<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=yUc7Cus2a-MC&pg=PA33&lpg=PA33&dq=It+is+the+second+largest+river+on+the+Indian+subcontinent+by+discharge&source=bl&ots=xr5fEOeB9U&sig=gN-NyIEvrRnho6_F0WjfKVEmrX0&hl=en&ei=VUysTd2GGcW3rAegx4CoCA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=10&ved=0CFkQ6AEwCQ#v=onepage&q&f=false The Ganga: water use in the Indian subcontinent] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=yUc7Cus2a-MC&pg=PA33&lpg=PA33&dq=It+is+the+second+largest+river+on+the+Indian+subcontinent+by+discharge&source=bl&ots=xr5fEOeB9U&sig=gN-NyIEvrRnho6_F0WjfKVEmrX0&hl=en&ei=VUysTd2GGcW3rAegx4CoCA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=10&ved=0CFkQ6AEwCQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20150401205952 }}, by Pranab Kumar Parua, p. 33</ref>。恆河流域為世界上最多人口居住的河流流域，共有4億以上人口居住於恆河流域，人口密度達每平方英里1000人以上<ref name="Arnold2000">{{cite book|last=Arnold|first=Guy|title=World strategic highways|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=FarwCNdYdmoC&pg=PA223|accessdate=26 April 2011|year=2000|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=9781579580988|pages=223–227|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308023702/https://books.google.com/books?id=FarwCNdYdmoC&pg=PA223|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

恆河被[[印度教|印度教]]徒視為聖河，也是河流周邊居民維持日常生活所需的命脈<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.zeenews.com/news587747.html |title=US TV host takes dig at Ganges |publisher=Zeenews.com |date=16 December 2009 |accessdate=4 July 2012 |archive-date=2009-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091218113826/http://www.zeenews.com/news587747.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印度教中也有稱為「[[恒河女神|恒河女神]]」的神祇<ref name="BhattacharjiBandyopadhyay1995">{{cite book|last1=Bhattacharji|first1=Sukumari|last2=Bandyopadhyay|first2=Ramananda|title=Legends of Devi|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=B0j0hRgWsg8C&pg=PA54|accessdate=27 April 2011|year=1995|publisher=Orient Blackswan|isbn=978-81-250-0781-4|page=54|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630064830/https://books.google.com/books?id=B0j0hRgWsg8C&pg=PA54|dead-url=no}}</ref>。許多過去的省會及帝國首都曾設於恆河沿岸，如[[巴连弗邑|巴连弗邑]]<ref name="Ghosh">{{cite book|last=Ghosh|first=A.|title=An encyclopaedia of Indian archaeology|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=law3AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA334|accessdate=27 April 2011|publisher=BRILL|oclc=313728835|isbn=978-90-04-09264-8|page=334|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630100245/https://books.google.com/books?id=law3AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA334|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[曲女城|曲女城]]<ref name="Ghosh"/>、[[瓦拉納西|瓦拉納西]]、[[安拉阿巴德|安拉阿巴德]]、[[穆尔斯希达巴德|穆尔斯希达巴德]]、[[蒙格埃尔|蒙格埃尔]]、[[巴哈拉姆普尔|巴哈拉姆普尔]]、[[加爾各答|加爾各答]]等。

恆河被評為世界五條污染最嚴重的河流之一<ref name=greendiary/>。在瓦拉納西所測得的水中糞生大腸桿菌群超過印度政府所訂標準值100倍以上<ref name=economist2008-ganges-pollution>[http://www.economist.com/world/asia/displaystory.cfm?story_id=11751397 "India and pollution: Up to their necks in it"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.economist.com/world/asia/displaystory.cfm?story_id=11751397 |date=20090612093603 }}, ''[[The_Economist|The Economist]]'', 27 July 2008.</ref>。污染不僅對人類造成危害，也對140種魚類、90種兩生類及瀕危的[[恆河豚|恆河豚]]造成威脅<ref name=greendiary>{{cite web |author=kalpana 1 Apr 2007 |url=http://www.greendiary.com/entry/ganga-is-dying-at-kanpur/ |title=Ganga is dying, pollution the killer |publisher=Greendiary.com |date=1 April 2007 |accessdate=4 July 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623121337/http://www.greendiary.com/entry/ganga-is-dying-at-kanpur |archivedate=2012年6月23日 }}</ref>。但以清理恆河為目標的「恆河治理計畫」<ref name=haberman>{{Citation|last=Haberman|first=David L.|title=River of love in an age of pollution:the Yamuna River of northern India|publisher=University of California Press. Pp. 277|year=2006|isbn=0-520-24790-6}}, page 160,</ref><ref name=gardner>{{Citation|last=Gardner|first=Gary|chapter=Engaging Religion in the Quest for a Sustainable World|pages=152–176|title=State of the World: 2003|editor-last=Bright|editor-first=Chris, et al|publisher=W. W. Norton & Company. Pp. 256|isbn=0-393-32386-2}}</ref><ref name=cleanperish>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-19/edit-page/28148254_1_national-river-conservation-plan-ganga-action-plan-ganga-and-yamuna "Clean Up Or Perish"] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-03-19/edit-page/28148254_1_national-river-conservation-plan-ganga-action-plan-ganga-and-yamuna |date=20111103162858 }}, ''The Times of India'', 19 March 2010</ref>，由於貪汙、技術不足<ref name=sheth>{{Citation|last=Sheth|first=Jagadish N.|title=Chindia Rising|publisher = Tata McGraw-Hill Education. Pp. 205|year = 2008|isbn=0-07-065708-4}}</ref>、缺乏良好環境計畫<ref name=singh>{{Citation|last1=Singh|first1=Munendra|last2=Singh|first2=Amit K.|title=Bibliography of Environmental Studies in Natural Characteristics and Anthropogenic Influences on the Ganga River|journal=Environ Monit Assess|year=2007|volume=129|pages=421–432|doi=10.1007/s10661-006-9374-7}}</ref>、印度傳統及信仰<ref name=tiwari>{{Citation|last=Tiwari|first=R. C.|chapter=Environmental Scenario in India|title=Explorations in Applied Geography|editor-last=Dutt|editor-first=Ashok K. et al|publisher=PHI Learning Pvt. Ltd. Pp. 524|isbn=81-203-3384-5|year=2008}}</ref>及缺乏宗教上有利支持<ref name=puttick3>{{Citation|last=Puttick|first=Elizabeth|chapter=Mother Ganges, India's Sacred River|year = 2008|title=The Healing Power of Water|editor-last=Emoto|editor-first=Masaru|publisher=Hay House Inc. Pp. 275|pages=241–252|isbn=1-4019-0877-2}}</ref>等因素，至今仍遭受重大挫敗。

==詞源==
恆河的[[梵語|梵語]]{{IAST|Gangā}}和[[英語|英語]]的come是同源詞，其本意就是速流、速去之河流，因含有速去速來、永無斷流的含義，漢地通譯爲恆河，意為“恆久之河”。唐代[[玄奘|玄奘]]法師譯名定爲“殑伽河”。此外還存在“弶伽河”、“恒伽河”<ref>比如[[东恒伽王朝|东恒伽王朝]]、[[西恒伽王朝|西恒伽王朝]]中的“恒伽”即半音半意譯自Ganga</ref>等等譯名。

==地理==
