==地質==
印度次大陸位於[[印度-澳洲板塊|印度-澳洲板塊]]中的次板塊[[印度板块|印度板块]]最北部<ref name=ali>{{cite journal
|last=Ali
|first=Jason R.
|coauthors=Jonathan C. Aitchison
|title=Greater India
|journal=Earth-Science Reviews
|volume=72
|issue=3–4
|year=2005
|pages=170–173
|doi=10.1016/j.earscirev.2005.07.005
|ref=ali}}</ref>。南方[[超大陸|超大陸]][[冈瓦那大陆|冈瓦那大陆]]的一部分於7,500萬年前開始向東北方移動，該地質作用約持續了5,000萬年，該大陸橫越了當時尚未形成的印度洋<ref name=ali/>。印度次大陸最終與[[歐亞大陸板塊|歐亞大陸板塊]]碰撞並[[隱沒帶|隱沒]]至歐亞板塊之下，抬升出地球上最高的山脈[[喜马拉雅山脉|喜马拉雅山脉]]<ref name=ali/>。在喜馬拉雅山形成時南麓曾存在大量因結構性下沉而出現的[[槽|槽]]地質構造，隨著[[印度河|印度河]]及恆河的沖積作用而逐漸被填滿<ref>{{Harvnb|Dikshit|Schwartzberg|2007|p=7.|Ref=dikshit}}</ref>，並形成現今的[[中央平原_(南亚)|印度平原]]<ref>{{cite journal
|last=Prakash
|first=B.
|coauthors=Sudhir Kumar, M. Someshwar Rao, S. C. Giri
|title=Holocene tectonic movements and stress field in the western Gangetic plains
|journal=Current Science
|volume=79
|issue=4
|year=2000
|pages=438–449
|url=http://www.ias.ac.in/currsci/aug252000/prakash.pdf
|format=PDF
|ref=harv
|access-date=2012-08-16
|archive-date=2011-05-04
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110504075319/http://www.ias.ac.in/currsci/aug252000/prakash.pdf
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，印度平原地質上則被認為是前淵或前陸台地<ref name="Dmowska2003">{{cite book|last=Dmowska|first=Renata|title=Advances in Geophysics|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ikFcqh1u1Q0C&pg=PA14|accessdate=6 May 2011|year=2003|publisher=Academic Press|isbn=978-0-12-018846-8|page=14|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630120531/https://books.google.com/books?id=ikFcqh1u1Q0C&pg=PA14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==文化==
{{Unreferencedsect}}
许多印度人出于信仰认为恒河发源于[[西藏|西藏]]的圣湖[[玛旁雍錯|玛旁雍錯]]，印度人称之为玛纳斯湖（Manasarowar），因而将之奉为圣河。他们认为浸在恒河中能把一个人的[[罪|罪]]洗去；把人[[火葬|火葬]]后的骨灰撒入河中，也有直接把死尸、遗物和葬礼物品直接抛入河中任其漂流的，认为这样能帮助死者得到更好的[[轮回|来世]]，甚至能更早获得“[[解脱|解脱]]”（Moksha）。很多虔诚的教徒都会往恒河[[朝圣|朝圣]]，并于河中浸浴及在河岸[[冥想|冥想]]。

是故由於上述難以收斂的傳統習慣，恆河的環境至今依然極度骯髒，经常是恒河里沐浴圣水者不远处就有漂流的浮尸经过，人们安之若素。

数个对[[印度教|印度教]]徒神圣的地点都位于恒河两岸，包括[[赫尔德瓦尔|赫尔德瓦尔]]及[[瓦拉纳西|瓦拉纳西]]。

==污染==
恆河污染程度相當嚴重，並影響了居住於河流附近的4億人口<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cleanganga.com/newsletter/index.php |title=June 2003 Newsletter |publisher=Clean Ganga |date= |accessdate=16 July 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090518135014/http://www.cleanganga.com/newsletter/index.php |archive-date=2009-05-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.time.com/time/health/article/0,8599,1581251,00.html | work=Time | title=The World's Dirty Rivers | date=22 January 2007 | accessdate=3 May 2010 | first=Elisabeth | last=Salemme | archive-date=2013-08-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825003132/http://www.time.com/time/health/article/0,8599,1581251,00.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。沿岸城市將廢水排入河道中，而由無法分解的塑膠所包裹的工業廢料及宗教祭品更加深了流經人口稠密區時所造成的污染<ref name=cleanperish/><ref name=Abraham>{{cite journal | last = Abraham | first = Wolf-Rainer | title = Review Article. Megacities as Sources for Pathogenic Bacteria in Rivers and Their Fate Downstream | url = http://www.hindawi.com/journals/ijmb/2011/798292/ | journal = International Journal of Microbiology | volume = 2011 | doi = 10.1155/2011/798292 | access-date = 2012-08-16 | archive-date = 2013-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131016113124/http://www.hindawi.com/journals/ijmb/2011/798292/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，河岸周邊貧窮人口藉河水沐浴、洗滌及烹煮也使水污染問題惡化<ref name=Abraham />。[[世界銀行|世界銀行]]估計印度水污染造成的保健費用約佔國內生產總值的3%<ref name=bharati>{{Citation|last=Bharati|first=Radha Kant|title=Interlinking of Indian rivers|publisher=Lotus Press. Pp. 129|year=2006|isbn=81-8382-041-7}}</ref>。報告指出印度八成的疾病及三分之一的死因與水傳疾病有關<ref>{{Citation|last=Puttick|first=Elizabeth|chapter=Mother Ganges, India's Sacred River|year = 2008|title=The Healing Power of Water|editor-last=Emoto|editor-first=Masaru|publisher=Hay House Inc. Pp. 275|pages=241–252|isbn=1-4019-0877-2}}</ref>。

